== 幕后 ==
2004年，编剧张永琛和历史学家王庆祥、东亚经贸新闻报社双方对峙法庭，原因是王庆祥发表文章《叹！史学家心血愤！名编剧剽窃》在该报社报纸上“诽谤”张永琛的“名誉权”，天津市高级人民法院判决王庆祥、东亚经贸新闻报社给张永琛赔偿经济损失人民币66万元，精神损失人民币1万元。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/ent/editor/tv/050515/050515_409238.html |title=《末代皇妃》名誉权案告终 张永琛获赔 |date=2005-05-15|accessdate=2014-03-12 |work=网易|archive-date=2014-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312212825/http://ent.163.com/ent/editor/tv/050515/050515_409238.html |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://culture.people.com.cn/GB/22219/3390291.html |title=《末代皇妃》名誉权侵权案告终|accessdate=2014-03-12 |date=2005-05-16 |work=人民网 |archive-date=2014-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312224635/http://culture.people.com.cn/GB/22219/3390291.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.sohu.com/20041014/n222488733.shtml |title=《末代皇妃》编剧诉名誉权受侵|accessdate=2014-03-12 |date=2004-10-14 |work=搜狐 |archive-date=2014-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312213124/http://news.sohu.com/20041014/n222488733.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.enorth.com.cn/system/2004/07/10/000817987.shtml |title=《末代皇妃》编剧张永琛郑重声明|accessdate=2014-03-12 |date=2004-07-10 |work=北方网 |archive-date=2014-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313001427/http://ent.enorth.com.cn/system/2004/07/10/000817987.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

